SDLC

Software Development Life Cycle

 

Presentation style of video.

Hit play, run me in the background, I’ll play this sound to indicate a change in slides, so you look at the screen.

Give a high level on what’s coming, then we’ll dive into more details about each step.

At each step, I’ll give you an example of how this was applied to Yaba.

At the end, you should have a better understanding of the SDLC.

As a side effect, you’ll understand better how Yaba works and is supposed to work.
